Hi guys,
Do you have a solution to batch upsert contacts AND associate with deals in only one request ?
I’ve did this, but the associations is not taken into account.
Am I missing something ?
```{
  "inputs": [
    {
      "idProperty": "email",
      "id": "<mailto:mail@mail.com|mail@mail.com>",
      "properties": {
        "firstname" : {firstname},
        "lastname" : {lastname},
      },
      "associations": [
        {
        "types": [
            {
            "associationCategory": "HubSpot_DEFINED",
            "associationTypeId": 4
            }
        ],
        "to": {
            "id": {deal_id}
            }
        }
    ]
    }
  ]
}```
